20:33.433 --> 20:34.834
I spoke to the head
of your order,

20:34.900 --> 20:37.133
Sister Leo Carria.

20:37.200 --> 20:40.533
She says you're questioning
your own vocation.

20:42.166 --> 20:44.266
- Yes, I am.

20:45.400 --> 20:46.934
- Welcome to the club.

20:47.000 --> 20:48.734
- You?

20:48.800 --> 20:52.000
- My first parish was way out
in the country,

20:52.066 --> 20:54.066
a desolate area.

20:54.133 --> 20:58.700
The pastor was old,
the housekeeper even older.

20:58.767 --> 21:01.533
When winter hit,
it was lonely.

21:01.600 --> 21:04.633
I cried...

21:04.700 --> 21:07.400
and I prayed.

21:07.467 --> 21:10.400
I cried some more...

21:10.467 --> 21:12.633
and prayed even harder.

21:12.700 --> 21:15.533
- Well, that's--
that's what I'm doing.

21:15.600 --> 21:17.967
- Good.

21:18.033 --> 21:21.633
Then whatever you decide
will be the right thing to do.

21:26.066 --> 21:28.033
- Thank you.

21:29.734 --> 21:32.533
- God bless you, Sister.

21:37.800 --> 21:39.800
- God bless you,
Sister.

21:42.266 --> 21:45.367
- As you already know, the jury
has ruled in our favor.

21:45.433 --> 21:49.467
They recognize that
the state was guilty

21:49.533 --> 21:52.934
in all injuries and deaths
caused after the riot.

21:53.000 --> 21:55.767
So they have made
recommendations

21:55.834 --> 21:58.567
that we receive
the full settlement:

21:58.633 --> 22:02.333
$45 million.

22:02.400 --> 22:03.800
- Oh, yeah!

22:03.867 --> 22:08.333
- Before you all go spending
that money, know this:

22:08.400 --> 22:10.066
the State has appealed
the decision.

22:10.133 --> 22:12.166
- Appealed?
- Yes, appealed.

22:12.233 --> 22:13.700
It is an election year.

22:13.767 --> 22:15.333
There is no way that Devlin
will write us a check,

22:15.400 --> 22:17.333
not before November.

22:17.400 --> 22:19.300
- Said, you can't goose
this thing along?

22:19.367 --> 22:21.333
- As we are all aware,

22:21.400 --> 22:22.700
the legal system
moves very slow.

22:22.767 --> 22:24.700
There's no way we can know
when our case is gonna be

22:24.767 --> 22:26.300
coming before
the appellate court.

22:26.367 --> 22:29.500
- Took almost 30 years for
the prisoners of Attica to win.

