they caught me.

45:25.967 --> 45:27.934
- You were standing outside
Miss Sally's house.

45:28.000 --> 45:30.367
- Yeah, I was hoping to catch
a glimpse of her in the flesh,

45:30.433 --> 45:32.567
maybe even exchange
a word or three.

45:32.633 --> 45:34.367
- What the fuck
happened to Alvarez?

45:34.433 --> 45:35.700
- I don't know.
Soon as we crawled

45:35.767 --> 45:37.333
