imperialism.

46:03.033 --> 46:05.333
- What do you miss most, Bob?

46:09.200 --> 46:12.000
- I have nothing
to say to you.

46:18.433 --> 46:20.900
- Bob, please, talk to me.

46:20.967 --> 46:23.400
This silence is grueling.

46:23.467 --> 46:25.100
Why are you mad at me?

46:25.200 --> 46:28.467
- The fact that you don't know
