47:20.600 --> 47:22.700
- Yeah, depresses
the fuck out of me.

47:25.500 --> 47:28.667
- Adebisi, weren't you
in love with Bellinger?

47:28.734 --> 47:29.934
- No.

47:30.000 --> 47:32.133
- Yeah, you had
