52:22.633 --> 52:25.233
Neither rain nor snow...

52:33.834 --> 52:35.200
Good-bye, Moses.

52:35.266 --> 52:37.400
- So long, Shirley.

52:37.467 --> 52:40.033
- See you around, kiddo.

52:40.100 --> 52:42.100
