55:51.000 --> 55:54.533
- The final act of mercy,
to bury the dead,

55:54.600 --> 55:57.367
to pray for the dead
and the living.

55:57.433 --> 55:59.567
We are merciful,

55:59.633 --> 56:01.834
not just for
humanitarian reasons.

56:01.900 --> 56:06.100
We are merciful because
we ourselves want to be saved.

56:06.166 --> 56:08.266
God expects mercy from us.

56:08.333 --> 56:10.300
God demands it.

56:10.367 --> 56:12.567
And how much mercy
does he show us?

56:14.233 --> 56:16.934
"Kyrie eleison"...

56:17.000 --> 56:20.967
